    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine shape\u2014no scratches, no weird noises, just pure driving bliss. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. If you're looking for that brand-new feel without the dealership headache, this is the one! Come take it for a spin!",
