    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines what it means to be 'pre-owned.' This car has been preserved in absolute showroom condition, having been strictly garage-kept and exclusively hand-washed since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark or stone chip, while the alloy wheels are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery still carries that distinctive new-car scent, and the bolsters show zero signs of entry or exit wear. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance with all services performed ahead of schedule. From the crisp response of the transmission to the silent, smooth idle of the engine, this car performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory. For the buyer who demands perfection and refuses to compromise on quality, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
