      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is basically flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved to pieces and is ready for a new adventure, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
